text: Squadron Leader John Leslie (Les) Munro CNZM, DSO, QSO, DFC, JP (born 5 April 1919 - 4 August 2015)New Zealand Stuff, Les Munro, last surviving Dam Buster dies was the last surviving pilot of the Dambusters Raid of May 1943. Munro was born in Gisborne, New Zealand. He died on 4 August 2015 in Tauranga, New Zealand at the age of 96. ==References== Category:1919 births Category:2015 deaths Category:Aviators Category:People from North Island Category:World War II people
